  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    IStaticReset

    public final class FilePublisherTask
extends com.ibm.team.build.internal.ant.AbstractContentPublisherTask
    Ant task to publish a file to a build result. The file is stored as content in a build result contribution.

    Required attributes are:

    • contributionTypeId - The extended contribution type id of this build result contribution.

    See AbstractContentPublisherTask for additional required and optional attributes.

    Since:
    0.5
